##  Development

### CSS Architecture
```text
assets/css/
 reset.css      # Normalize and reset styles
 variables.css  # Design system tokens
 base.css       # Base typography and utilities
 components.css # Reusable UI components
 layouts.css    # Section-specific layouts
 animations.css # Animation definitions
```

### JavaScript Modules
```text
assets/js/
 main.js         # Core functionality and interactions
 data-loader.js  # Dynamic content loading
 performance.js  # Performance optimizations
```

### Content Management
Content is managed through `assets/data/content.json` for easy updates without touching HTML.

##  Key Features Explained

### Theme System
- Automatic system preference detection
- Manual toggle with persistence
- Smooth transitions between themes
- CSS custom properties for easy customization

### Animation System
- Scroll-triggered animations using Intersection Observer
- CSS animations with reduced motion support
- Progressive enhancement approach

### Performance Optimizations
- Critical CSS inlined
- Non-critical resources lazy loaded
- Service worker for caching
- Optimized images and assets

